data.description: CUSTOM 2-STORY BRICK AND VINYL CONSTRUCTION BACK IN 2005! LOCATED ON A DEAD-END BLOCK & IS ADJACENT TO A SCHOOL, THE HOME OFFERS LOTS OF PRIVACY. MASSIVE 2,594SF 6 BEDROOM, 3 1/2 BATH HAS ENOUGH ROOM TO ACCOMMODATE A LARGE OR EVEN EXTENDED FAMILY. ENTERING THE BEAUTIFUL HOME YOU'LL ENJOY THE SOARING 2-STORY CEILING IN THE FOYER & LIVING ROOM. WALKING INTO THE KITCHEN WITH ENOUGH ROOM FOR A CHEF, 32&36" OAK CABINETS/L-SHAPED COUNTERTOPS W/BREAKFAST BAR AREA & STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES AWAIT. OVERLOOKING THE KITCHEN IS THE 21X18 FAMILY ROOM COMPLETE WITH BRICK FIREPLACE & EXPANSIVE VIEWS OF THE BACKYARD. 4 BEDROOMS ARE LOCATED UPSTAIRS INCLUDING PRIMARY BEDROOM THAT INCLUDES TREYED CEILING/ROW OF WINDOWS, WALK IN CLOSET & PRIVATE, PRIMARY BATHROOM W/JETTED TUB & SEPARATE SHOWER. FULL, FINISHED BASEMENT INCLUDES 2 ADDL ROOMS, BONUS ROOM & FULL BATH ALONG WITH STORAGE ROOM. FURNACE REPLACED IN 2020, SUMP PUMPS REPLACED 2021. LARGE DECK OFF THE REAR OF THE HOME OVERLOOKS FULLY, FENCED YARD.
